<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Theatre seat, broken in two halves (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.37</measure> x  D. 0.69, total W. c. 130).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>Inscribed, i on the seat; ii on the riser.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>i in a large sprawling hand, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.18</measure>; ; ii regular formal lettering, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.03</measure>; ΝΗ in ligature.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notBefore="0101" notAfter="0600" exact="none">Second to sixth centuries A.D.</date> (<rs type="criteria">context</rs>)
</p>
</div>
